org.ow2.proactive.resourcemanager.nodesource

Interface NodeSourcePlugin

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AutoUpdateInfrastructure, BatchJobInfrastructure, CLIInfrastructure, CronPolicy, DefaultInfrastructureManager, EmptyPolicy, GenericBatchJobInfrastructure, HostsFileBasedInfrastructureManager, InfrastructureAwarePolicy, InfrastructureManager, LocalInfrastructure, LSFInfrastructure, NodeSourcePolicy, PBSInfrastructure, RestartDownNodesPolicy, RMAwareNodeSourcePolicy, SSHInfrastructure, SSHInfrastructureV2, StaticPolicy, TimeSlotPolicy

    public interface NodeSourcePlugin
extends Serializable
    Common interface to the classes that can be plugged in as an infrastructure or policy of a node source. Parsing of the Configurable fields of a Plugin class is the same whether the concrete class is an infrastructure or a policy.
